### Genfeed API - Public Brands Endpoints
### Public brand profiles, media, and links (no authentication required)
### All endpoints are @Public() - no Authorization header needed

########################################
# Public Brand Discovery
########################################

### Get Public Brands
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/public/brands


### Get Highlighted Brands
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/public/brands?isHighlighted=true&limit=10


### Get Public Brands with Custom Limit
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/public/brands?limit=50


### Get Brand by Handle
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/public/brands/handle?handle={{testBrandHandle}}


########################################
# Single Brand
########################################

### Get Brand by ID
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/public/brands/{{testBrandId}}


########################################
# Brand Content
########################################

### Get Brand Links
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/public/brands/{{testBrandId}}/links


### Get Brand Videos
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/public/brands/{{testBrandId}}/videos


### Get Brand Videos with Pagination
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/public/brands/{{testBrandId}}/videos?page=1&limit=20&sort=-createdAt


### Get Brand Images
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/public/brands/{{testBrandId}}/images


### Get Brand Images with Pagination
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/public/brands/{{testBrandId}}/images?page=1&limit=20&sort=-createdAt


### Get Brand Articles
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/public/brands/{{testBrandId}}/articles


### Get Brand Articles with Pagination
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/public/brands/{{testBrandId}}/articles?page=1&limit=20&sort=-createdAt


########################################
# Test Cases
########################################

### Test: Brand Not Found
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/public/brands/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011


### Test: Invalid Brand ID Format
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/public/brands/invalid-id


### Test: Handle Not Found
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/public/brands/handle?handle=nonexistent-brand


### Test: Handle Not Provided
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/public/brands/handle
